{"tid":1055401,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律人士請入] 急，有關遺產託管問題","createTime":"2019-03-10T13:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T15:07:58.000Z","uid":79627,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"36dd3ba6b12e8af2c6f58ed5ab0866637b382d81","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"冇分台冇人睇到，現重開<br />\n<br />\n大家好，想問下有冇法律jj 可以解釋吓<br />\n遺產受益人可唔可以同事兼任另一受益人嗰part 遺產嘅託管人<br />\n因為我(A) 已成年，但(B) 未成年，身邊最friend 嘅朋友幫忙draft 咗份遺囑，見證人同託管人都係(C)同(D)，媽媽最親嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n但係身邊有親戚話放人之心不可無，驚第日有爭拗，問可唔可以我託管B嗰part 嘅遺產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbbc93db85ce2ee8cbd7f0fd1447e8304cba0e6","tid":1055401,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"約律師比顧問費<br />\n連登仔答你yes/no都無用"},{"pid":"83b76393f48bf29682c90d99ad1156d10e23a217","tid":1055401,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"100%<br />\n可以"},{"pid":"20c54cc5eb79e8a15e4ee8cc815637630fb95007","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffbbc93db85ce2ee8cbd7f0fd1447e8304cba0e6","tid":1055401,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"約律師比顧問費<br />\n連登仔答你yes/no都無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"係，我都知道，我而家喺醫院過夜行唔開心急先開post 問吓，唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47767115b7c6a3869479b7accfa27fa1b205e7d0","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83b76393f48bf29682c90d99ad1156d10e23a217","tid":1055401,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"100%<br />\n可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:33:26.000Z","msg":"即係我可以做受益人+B嗰份嘅託管人 正確?<br />\n<br />\n請問絲打係律師定師爺定之類，唔係問完又唔信，得個知字<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f6d32cf21e3a91a190816bdfe52c1c30c47da3","tid":1055401,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"你有咁多資產要信託，都慳果少少律師費"},{"pid":"2a31018b3e9513db907608d277913ff1fc608369","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01f6d32cf21e3a91a190816bdfe52c1c30c47da3","tid":1055401,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"你有咁多資產要信託，都慳果少少律師費"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"唔係唔係，窮人嚟<br />\n只係未夠18歲要人託管，<br />\n&quot;vi)\t分配遺產<br />\n<br />\n分配年齡：如遺產受益人未滿18 歲，遺囑執行人必須以信託形式持有該受益人的遺產（即代該未成年人妥善地保管有關遺產）。有些父母也可能會在遺囑上列明，子女須在更年長及較成熟時（ 如年滿 21 或 25 歲）才可繼承遺產。所以，遺囑執行人亦可以有酌情權，在子女正式能夠取得所有遺產前，適當地向他 / 她分發若干金額作為日常生活開支。<br />\n&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkclic.org/tc/topics/probate/making_a_will/q2.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkclic.org%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2Fprobate%2Fmaking_a_will%2Fq2.shtml&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=d4bf2a37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkclic.org/tc/topics/probate/making_a_will/q2.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n今日太忙碌所以情急先上嚟問咗先，唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b04c15dd93f38fd6a63af36429ea10f3678164f","tid":1055401,"uid":20857,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"36dd3ba6b12e8af2c6f58ed5ab0866637b382d81","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"冇分台冇人睇到，現重開<br />\n<br />\n大家好，想問下有冇法律jj 可以解釋吓<br />\n遺產受益人可唔可以同事兼任另一受益人嗰part 遺產嘅託管人<br />\n因為我(A) 已成年，但(B) 未成年，身邊最friend 嘅朋友幫忙draft 咗份遺囑，見證人同託管人都係(C)同(D)，媽媽最親嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n但係身邊有親戚話放人之心不可無，驚第日有爭拗，問可唔可以我託管B嗰part 嘅遺產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"Executor 可以同時係 beneficiary。以你嗰講法，你可以同時託管遺產同受益，而份遺囑唔會因此無效。<br />\n<br />\n利申：trainee solicitor."},{"pid":"fe8652b14d559613e5b870b7e2429483e2caac54","tid":1055401,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47767115b7c6a3869479b7accfa27fa1b205e7d0","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83b76393f48bf29682c90d99ad1156d10e23a217","tid":1055401,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"100%<br />\n可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:33:26.000Z","msg":"即係我可以做受益人+B嗰份嘅託管人 正確?<br />\n<br />\n請問絲打係律師定師爺定之類，唔係問完又唔信，得個知字<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"我係想講<br />\n我話係你就信?<br />\n我fake你點算?<br />\n去D區議員度問下唔洗錢"},{"pid":"631cb7e3ad9d34efd4d3aaccc868409a31b17b1c","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b04c15dd93f38fd6a63af36429ea10f3678164f","tid":1055401,"uid":20857,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"36dd3ba6b12e8af2c6f58ed5ab0866637b382d81","tid":1055401,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"冇分台冇人睇到，現重開<br />\n<br />\n大家好，想問下有冇法律jj 可以解釋吓<br />\n遺產受益人可唔可以同事兼任另一受益人嗰part 遺產嘅託管人<br />\n因為我(A) 已成年，但(B) 未成年，身邊最friend 嘅朋友幫忙draft 咗份遺囑，見證人同託管人都係(C)同(D)，媽媽最親嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n但係身邊有親戚話放人之心不可無，驚第日有爭拗，問可唔可以我託管B嗰part 嘅遺產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"Executor 可以同時係 beneficiary。以你嗰講法，你可以同時託管遺產同受益，而份遺囑唔會因此無效。<br />\n<br />\n利申：trainee solicitor."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:03:43.000